name: Simorgh, Bird of Endings
desc: When this card is Normal Summoned: You can send 1 "Simorgh" card from your Deck to the GY, except "Simorgh, Bird of Endings". If your opponent controls no cards in their Spell & Trap Zones and this card is in your GY: You can activate this effect; you cannot Special Summon monsters for the rest of this turn, except Winged Beast monsters, also Special Summon this card in Defense Position, but banish it if it leaves the field. You can only use each effect of "Simorgh, Bird of Endings" once per turn.
str1: Send from deck to the GY
